Pagezii chrome extension is a powerful on-Page SEO analysis tool. It's specifically designed for SEO Managers who want to optimize their organic traffic. The Pagezii Chrome Extension is completely free and offers the following: 

- Single click Analysis
- Quick overall SEO Score
- Page and Ad Message breakdown
- Reader Profiles
- Detailed SEO attributes

The tool is designed for SEO Managers to keep track of their on-page SEO as well as review competitor pages for on-page SEO.
